 pokój,"}]},{"align":"","text":[{"style":"","value":"w znaku wiary zjednoczą cały świat."}]},{"align":"","text":[{"style":"","value":"Nowi ludzie przyniosą ziemi wolność,"}]},{"align":"","text":[{"style":"","value":"prawda ludzi wyzwoli, niszcząc zło."}]}]}],"globalGroup":"verse"}},"layouts":{"0797ae1107f":{"name":"Domyślne","notes":"","slides":[{"id":"797ae1107fb"},{"id":"97ae1107fb1"},{"id":"7ae1107fb1d"},{"id":"ae1107fb1df"}]}},"media":{}}]